{{Flavour|Summons one or more earth elementals.}}

'''Summon Earth Elementals''' is a monster-only spell that summons [[earth elemental|earth elementals]] to the caster's aid.

The following enemies cast Summon Earth Elementals:
*{{monsterlink|Deep elf mage}}

==History==
*Prior to [[0.27]], [[deep elf mage|deep elf magi]] had this spell.

